---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page title="Ultimate Security Solutions | Elite Security & IT Infrastructure">
    <header style="position:relative; min-height:92vh; display:flex; align-items:center; z-index:1;">
        <div style="position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; height:200px; background:linear-gradient(to top, var(--primary), transparent); z-index:2; pointer-events:none;"></div>
        <div class="container" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:center; position:relative; z-index:3; padding:8rem 2rem 4rem;">
            <div style="animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;">
                <div style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem; background:var(--accent-dim); color:var(--accent); padding:0.5rem 1.25rem; border:1px solid var(--border-hover); font-weight:700; font-size:0.7rem; letter-spacing:2px; border-radius:100px; margin-bottom:2rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i> VETERAN OWNED &bull; COMMERCIAL ONLY
                </div>
                <h1 style="margin-bottom:1.5rem; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 40%, var(--accent) 100%); -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; background-clip:text;">
                    ULTIMATE<br><span class="text-accent">SECURITY</span><br>SOLUTIONS
                </h1>
                <p style="font-size:1.15rem; color:var(--muted); max-width:560px; margin-bottom:2.5rem; line-height:1.8;">
                    Specialized subcontracting for MSPs and enterprise clients. White-label smart hands, structured cabling, and physical security infrastructure with military-grade precision.
                </p>
                <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                    <a href="/ordering-system" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Hardware Catalog</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Request a Quote</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;">
                <div style="width:280px; height:280px; border-radius:50%; background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,215,0,0.1), transparent 60%); border:2px solid var(--border-hover); display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; position:relative;">
                    <div style="position:absolute; inset:-20px; border-radius:50%; border:1px solid var(--border); animation:pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-halved" style="font-size:7rem; color:var(--accent); opacity:0.3;"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="stats-grid" style="border-top:1px solid var(--border); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="stat-block"><div class="stat-num">500+</div><div class="stat-label">Deployments</div></div>
        <div class="stat-block"><div class="stat-num">100mi</div><div class="stat-label">Service Radius</div></div>
        <div class="stat-block"><div class="stat-num">99.9%</div><div class="stat-label">Uptime SLA</div></div>
        <div class="stat-block"><div class="stat-num">24/7</div><div class="stat-label">Rapid Response</div></div>
    </div>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
            <h2 class="section-title anim">CORE CAPABILITIES</h2>
            <p class="anim" style="color:var(--muted); max-width:600px; margin:-0.5rem auto 0;">Mission-critical infrastructure built on discipline, precision, and technical mastery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-auto">
            <a href="/accomplishments" class="card anim"><i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i><h3>Structured Cabling</h3><p>Cat6 infrastructure with certified testing and TIA-606-C labeling for data centers and commercial spaces.</p></a>
            <a href="/ordering-system?cat=camera" class="card anim"><i class="fas fa-video"></i><h3>CCTV Surveillance</h3><p>AI-powered analytics, LPR, and commercial NVR deployment for 24/7 asset protection.</p></a>
            <a href="/ordering-system?cat=ubiquiti" class="card anim"><i class="fas fa-server"></i><h3>Network Engineering</h3><p>IDF/MDF cleanups, rack stack, and enterprise switching. Smart hands for MSPs.</p></a>
            <a href="/ordering-system?cat=access" class="card anim"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i><h3>Access Control</h3><p>Biometric, card-based, and mobile entry systems for secure facilities.</p></a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-glow" style="text-align:center;">
        <h2 class="anim" style="color:var(--accent);">READY TO UPGRADE?</h2>
        <p class="anim" style="color:var(--muted); max-width:600px; margin:0 auto 2rem;">From single-site installs to multi-location rollouts, we deliver on time and on budget.</p>
        <div class="anim" style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Get Started</a>
            <a href="/system-design" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i> USS Suite</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container" style="text-align:center;"><h2 class="section-title anim">MISSION SUCCESS</h2></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px,1fr)); gap:1.5rem; margin-top:3rem;">
                <div class="testimonial anim"><i class="fas fa-quote-left" style="color:var(--accent); opacity:0.4; margin-bottom:1rem;"></i><p class="quote">"Ultimate Security Solutions was the perfect partner to have on our Access Control project. They went above and beyond."</p><p class="author">- Zachary Harmison</p></div>
                <div class="testimonial anim"><i class="fas fa-quote-left" style="color:var(--accent); opacity:0.4; margin-bottom:1rem;"></i><p class="quote">"Consistently excellent work. Very knowledgeable with electronics, electrical and networking."</p><p class="author">- Senior IT Support, Video Mining Corp</p></div>
                <div class="testimonial anim"><i class="fas fa-quote-left" style="color:var(--accent); opacity:0.4; margin-bottom:1rem;"></i><p class="quote">"They accommodate our tight schedule with ease. A very diligent team, knowledgeable and thorough!"</p><p class="author">- Operations Manager</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="text-align:center;">
        <h2 class="section-title anim">SECURE YOUR ASSETS</h2>
        <div class="anim" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:2rem; max-width:800px; margin:3rem auto 0;">
            <div><i class="fas fa-phone-alt" style="font-size:1.5rem; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:block;"></i><h3 style="font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Call Us</h3><p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:0.9rem;">816-814-2007</p></div>
            <div><i class="fas fa-envelope" style="font-size:1.5rem; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:block;"></i><h3 style="font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Email</h3><p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:0.9rem;">admin@usstech.net</p></div>
            <div><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" style="font-size:1.5rem; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:block;"></i><h3 style="font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Service Area</h3><p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:0.9rem;">KC Metro (100mi)</p></div>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary anim" style="margin-top:2rem;"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Request a Quote</a>
    </section>
</Page>

<style>
    @media (max-width:1024px) {
        header div.container { grid-template-columns:1fr!important; text-align:center; }
        header div.container > div:first-child { max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; }
        header div.container > div:first-child p { margin:0 auto 2.5rem; }
        header div.container > div:last-child { display:none; }
    }
</style>
